---
title: Tahini & Honey-Glazed Pork with Wedges, Pickled Onion Salad & Pine Nuts
description: Tahini is such a versatile and delicious ingredient, it's almost impossible to stop ourselves from adding it to every dish. In this case, exceptions had to be made. We combined tahini dressing with honey to make a mouth-watering glaze for these juicy pork loin steaks, and the result; a humble dinner, quickly turned showstopper to say the least.
